There is already an article which sings praises to Ruby. And so does the author of Sonic Pi.
 Amazingly, the concept of programming is probably emerged along with the first musical machines. These days, I see how code becomes the universal language which gets ideas across when nothing else can. And the music is the code of feelings. Except when you have &ldquo;amusia.&rdquo;
Today I got curious to explore Sonic Pi and its integration with DAW via MIDI in particular.
